fields.name: Diggin’ Black Hoddie
fields.description: Our Diggin’ black hoodies are comfortable and durable. Made from 80% cotton and 20% polyester, it is comfortable to wear and soft to the skin. The twin-needle stitching throughout provides added strength to the garment, ensuring it will last wash after wash. Its ribbed hem and cuff finishings with Lycra also ensure this product retains its shape wash after wash. Perfect for on or off the bike!

fields.name: Danny MacAskill
fields.description: Daniel "Danny" MacAskill is a Scottish trials cyclist, from Dunvegan on the Isle of Skye. He works professionally as a street trials / Mountain bike rider for Santa Cruz Bicycles. In April 2009, he released a five-minute street trials video to YouTube, filmed by his flatmate Dave Sowerby.

fields.name: Brandon Semenuk
fields.description: Brandon Semenuk is a Canadian freeride mountain biker and rally racer from Whistler, British Columbia. Semenuk is a three-time Freeride Mountain Bike World Tour Gold Medalist. He is a five-time Red Bull Joyride winner, X-Games Real MTB Gold Medalist, and X-Games Silver medalist in the Mountain Bike Slopestyle event.

fields.name: Sam Reynolds
fields.description: Sam Reynolds is a Professional freeride Mountain biker. Known for his Best Trick award in 2015 Red Bull Rampage event when he did a superman over a 72'ft Canyon Gap. He also later performed a trick the "rock solid" in the same event.
